    "detail": "I have been staying in many kinds of hotels no matter for business or travel, I must say this is one of the best hotel I have stayed. I don't need it to be five stars, this hotel is just cozy and confortable. I have a wide balcony at room facing street. They got unique and modern design for guestroom and it's very users friendly. Room size is nice. The only bad thing is there's no sliding door or curtain at shower room so the floor became all wet after showers. Two metro stations in 5mins walk. Supermarket and convenient stores are all nearby. A few restaurants are downstairs and so many more one and two blocks away next to the square. This area is peaceful for vocation and it's convenient to reach the heart of Paris. Staff are friendly and willing to help. Love this hotel:)",
